leve.name: Picking Up the Piercers
leve.description: The Wood Wailers seek volunteers to locate and collect practice spears left in the field after a large-scale training exercise held two days past. Those accepting the task are recommended to arm themselves, as the area in question is known to be populated with dangerous creatures.
leve.client: 1st Bow of the Quiver's Centaurs, Galfrid Mossback
